data.description: Beautiful country home located in the northern part of Giles County on almost an acre and in the Richland School District.  This very well maintained home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, great room over the garage and a gorgeous granite kitchen. It has an oversized 2 car garage, concrete driveway, storage building, dog run, covered front and back porches and a crawlspace that you can stand in. Very close to the historic Milky Way Farms. Wonderful location in Eagles Pointe! Conveniently located between Nashville and Huntsville.
